; Optical constants file
;
; File: Al2O3.nkv
;
; Material: Sapphire, Al2O3
;
; Calculated using the dispersion formulas from
; I. H. Malitson and M. J. Dodge. Refractive Index and Birefringence of Synthetic Sapphire, J. Opt. Soc. Am. 62, 1405 (1972)
; obtained at https://refractiveindex.info/?shelf=main&book=Al2O3&page=Malitson-o
;
;
; Wavelength range [nm]: [200:1:2000]
;
; Author: IR-S
;
; Date: 20/03/2017
;
; Comments:
; This is a birefringent material so there are formulas for
; no (n for ordinary ray) and ne (n for extraordinary ray).
; We calculate n as the average of ne and no.
;
;
;
; Lambda (nm)   n            k
